      "path": "audio/narrations/sorting-algorithms/xiaoxiao/intro-intro-1.mp3",
      "duration": 1.99,
      "size": 31824,
      "text": "桌上有一排高矮不一的柱子，我们想把它们从矮到高排好。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "sorting-algorithms",
      "section_id": "intro",
      "line_id": "intro-2",
      "filename": "intro-intro-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/sorting-algorithms/xiaoxiao/intro-intro-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.12,
      "size": 33840,
      "text": "计算机每天都在做这件事：把杂乱的数据变得井然有序。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "sorting-algorithms",
      "section_id": "intro",
      "line_id": "intro-3",
      "filename": "intro-intro-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/sorting-algorithms/xiaoxiao/intro-intro-3.mp3",
      "duration": 1.71,
      "size": 27360,
      "text": "同样是排序，方法不同，快慢却相差巨大。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "sorting-algorithms",
      "section_id": "basic",
      "line_id": "def-1",
      "filename": "basic-def-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/sorting-algorithms/xiaoxiao/basic-def-1.mp3",
      "duration": 2.43,
      "size": 38880,
      "text": "冒泡排序相邻两两比较，大的往后挪，每一轮把最大值送到末尾。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "sorting-algorithms",
      "section_id": "basic",
      "line_id": "def-2",
      "filename": "basic-def-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/sorting-algorithms/xiaoxiao/basic-def-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.29,
      "size": 36576,
      "text": "插入排序像整理扑克牌，把每张牌插进前面已排好的部分。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "sorting-algorithms",
      "section_id": "basic",
      "line_id": "def-3",
      "filename": "basic-def-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/sorting-algorithms/xiaoxiao/basic-def-3.mp3",
      "duration": 2.12,
      "size": 33840,
      "text": "它们直观易懂，但都要两层循环，复杂度是 O(n 的平方)。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "sorting-algorithms",
      "section_id": "quick",
      "line_id": "quick-1",
      "filename": "quick-quick-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/sorting-algorithms/xiaoxiao/quick-quick-1.mp3",
      "duration": 1.96,
      "size": 31392,
      "text": "快排选一个基准，把比它小的放左边，比它大的放右边。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "sorting-algorithms",
      "section_id": "quick",
      "line_id": "quick-2",
      "filename": "quick-quick-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/sorting-algorithms/xiaoxiao/quick-quick-2.mp3",
      "duration": 1.92,
      "size": 30672,
      "text": "再对左右两半递归地做同样的事，这就是分而治之。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "sorting-algorithms",
      "section_id": "quick",
      "line_id": "quick-3",
      "filename": "quick-quick-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/sorting-algorithms/xiaoxiao/quick-quick-3.mp3",
      "duration": 1.77,
      "size": 28368,
      "text": "平均下来只需 O(n 乘以 log n)，比冒泡快得多。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "sorting-algorithms",
      "section_id": "merge",
      "line_id": "merge-1",
      "filename": "merge-merge-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/sorting-algorithms/xiaoxiao/merge-merge-1.mp3",
      "duration": 2.04,
      "size": 32688,
      "text": "归并排序先把数组一分为二，直到每段只剩一个元素。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "sorting-algorithms",
      "section_id": "merge",
      "line_id": "merge-2",
      "filename": "merge-merge-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/sorting-algorithms/xiaoxiao/merge-merge-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.33,
      "size": 37296,
      "text": "再两两合并有序的小段，相等元素保持原序，因此它很稳定。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "sorting-algorithms",
      "section_id": "interaction",
      "line_id": "int-1",
      "filename": "interaction-int-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/sorting-algorithms/xiaoxiao/interaction-int-1.mp3",
      "duration": 1.63,
      "size": 26064,
      "text": "选择一种算法，单步观察每一次比较和交换。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "sorting-algorithms",
      "section_id": "interaction",
      "line_id": "int-2",
      "filename": "interaction-int-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/sorting-algorithms/xiaoxiao/interaction-int-2.mp3",
      "duration": 1.83,
      "size": 29232,
      "text": "也可以点击播放，让柱子在动画里自己排好队。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "sorting-algorithms",
      "section_id": "summary",
      "line_id": "sum-1",
